                        <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Sprint:</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_10020-252513-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%">April 1 Release</td>
            </tr>
                                <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Rank:</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_10019-252513-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%">      0|r0poul:y
  </td>
            </tr>
                                <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Release Notes:</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_11841-252513-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%">      <p>In December 2025, the abstraction team added a new variable to capture the date of a patient's last oncology-specific healthcare. 
    <span class="jira-issue-macro" data-jira-key="ADS-375" >
                <a href="https://n-power.atlassian.net/browse/ADS-375" class="jira-issue-macro-key issue-link"  title="Add last health system encounter date" >
            <img class="icon" src="https://n-power.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10321?size=medium" />
            ADS-375
        </a>
                                                    <span class="aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-current jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">QC</span>
            </span>
 involved bringing in this new variable, which required minor tweaking to ensure patient rows were also prioritized to be kept if they had values for this new variable too. The final variable added to the enriched ADS cohort was last_oncology_encounter_date; last_abstraction_date was only very minimally impacted (n&lt;10 changes across the 4 cohorts). The internal variables last_hs_interaction_abstracted_date and last_hs_interaction_structured_date were kept internal and were also only minimally impacted. </p>
  </td>
            </tr>
                                <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Code Review:</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_12225-252513-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%"><div class="shorten" id="customfield_12225-field">
                        <span class="tinylink">        <span class="user-hover" rel="ug:122d8429-4cb9-4247-8547-aa472f2bdbd8" id="multiuser_cf_ug:122d8429-4cb9-4247-8547-aa472f2bdbd8">Brian Carter</span></span>            </div>
</td>
            </tr>
                                <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Release Priority:</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_12224-252513-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%">    High - required for customer need, blocker for future dev, bug
</td>
            </tr>
                                <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Data Review (migrated):</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_12226-252513-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%"><div class="shorten" id="customfield_12226-field">
                        <span class="tinylink">        <span class="user-hover" rel="b3a562d6-6e2a-4835-a18d-c160b27567ce" id="multiuser_cf_b3a562d6-6e2a-4835-a18d-c160b27567ce">Monika Izano</span></span>            </div>
